Class RecvIndTask

    • popt4jlib.PS.RecvIndTask

    public class RecvIndTask
extends java.lang.Object
implements TaskObject
    used in migrating individuals between islands in DPSO (or other ps-based approaches, eg FA). Not part of the public API (though the class is public as it is also used from the FA sub-package).
